#### 7. **Initial Frames Drop During Startup (Optional)**
If needed for stabilization, drop initial frames in a background task before enabling full functionality.

```cpp
xTaskCreate(
    [](void* arg) {
        Esp32Camera* self = static_cast<Esp32Camera*>(arg);
        // Capture and discard frames for e.g. 5 seconds
        ...
        self->streaming_on_ = true;
        vTaskDelete(NULL);
    },
    "CameraInitTask", 4096, this, 5, nullptr);
```

